{"tid":2063783,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲報咗任何Business School","createTime":"2020-06-14T09:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T07:30:42.000Z","uid":172141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"702aade52465f82bc43ab693cc25115d1a07c8db","tid":2063783,"uid":172141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:40:31.000Z","msg":"（包括本地同埋外國）小弟有幾條問題：<br />\n1. 報咗咩大學同埋咩科<br />\n2. 想知道大家收倒offer/interview完未<br />\n3. 承上題，等咗幾耐先有/報咗幾耐都未有回音<br />\n4. 如果係有offer或者面試既話想知道報咗邊啲學校同埋本身用咩報（undergraduate, GMAT/GRE, 有幾多年工作經驗）<br />\n5. 如果有scholarship你地會留定係走（你當兩間學校差唔多名氣）<br />\n<br />\n而家每日等到頸都長所以想請教各位大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b26aaca9baf8331fe0bf05fcddf47a32175e024","tid":2063783,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T11:09:45.000Z","msg":"DSE or non dse ar diu"},{"pid":"50f10d2855372ad36c8122aa0ffa755e5936069c","tid":2063783,"uid":172141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b26aaca9baf8331fe0bf05fcddf47a32175e024","tid":2063783,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T11:09:45.000Z","msg":"DSE or non dse ar diu"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:29:38.000Z","msg":"Postgrad"},{"pid":"b19c474446281bc2a9ff6e9ac48941ff7cc9792d","tid":2063783,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50f10d2855372ad36c8122aa0ffa755e5936069c","tid":2063783,"uid":172141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b26aaca9baf8331fe0bf05fcddf47a32175e024","tid":2063783,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T11:09:45.000Z","msg":"DSE or non dse ar diu"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:29:38.000Z","msg":"Postgrad"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />grad school<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6805ae38bd0584d511cbffc3842370c6fb3440e",